Affiliation = {Xiong, J (Corresponding Author), Southwest Jiaotong Univ, Sch Mat Sci \& Engn, Key Lab Adv Technol Mat, Minist Educ, 111,Sect 1 North Second Ring Rd, Chengdu 610031, Peoples R China.
