   Ding, Zhao; Li, Yuting; Jiang, Han; Wan, Haiyi; Qiu, Junqi; Jiang, Fangning; Tan, Jun; Chen, Yu'an; Pan, Fusheng, Chongqing Univ, Coll Mat Sci \& Engn, Natl Engn Res Ctr Magnesium Alloys, Natl Innovat Ctr Ind Educ Integrat Energy Storage, Chongqing 400044, Peoples R China.
   Zhou, Yang, Wuhan Text Univ, Sch Text Sci \& Engn, State Key Lab New Text Mat \& Adv Proc Technol, Wuhan 430200, Peoples R China.
   Du, Wenjia, Univ Oxford, Dept Engn Sci, Oxford, England.
   Shaw, Leon L., IIT, Dept Mech Mat \& Aerosp Engn, Chicago, IL 60616 USA.},
DOI = {10.1002/idm2.12216},
