   Jeong, Nohyeong; Chen, Yongsheng, Georgia Inst Technol, Sch Civil \& Environm Engn, Atlanta, GA 30332 USA.
   Park, Shinyun; Blotevogel, Jens; Tong, Tiezheng, Colorado State Univ, Dept Civil \& Environm Engn, Ft Collins, CO 80523 USA.
