   Jaffrelot and Sturlese, Mattia and Sosic, Alice and Volpiana, Martina
   and Lugato, Angela and Barone, Marco and Gatto, Barbara and Macchia,
   Maria Ludovica and Bellanda, Massimo and Battistutta, Roberto and
   Salata, Cristiano and Kondratov, Ivan and Iminov, Rustam and Khairulin,
