   Tsunegi, Sumito; Taniguchi, Tomohiro, Natl Inst Adv Ind Sci \& Technol, Res Ctr Emerging Comp Technol, Tsukuba, Ibaraki 3058568, Japan.
   Nishida, Mitsuhiro; Sakurai, Ryo, Bridgestone Corp, Digital Engn Div, Tokyo 1048340, Japan.
   Wakao, Yasumichi, Bridgestone Corp, Adv Mat Div, Tokyo 1048340, Japan.},
DOI = {10.1002/aisy.202200123},
EarlyAccessDate = {SEP 2022},
