   Wu, Kai; Wu, Peng; Li, Zhe; Kong, Sijia; Yu, Lu; Zhang, Enpu; Liu, Hanlin; Guo, Qing, Luohu Hosp Grp, Shenzhen Following Precis Med Res Inst, Shenzhen 518001, Peoples R China.
