   Karmi, Yacine, Univ Constantine 1, Inst Appl Sci \& Tech, Electromech Dept, Constantine, Algeria.
   Hammoudi, Abderazek, Mhamed Bougara Univ, UR MPE, Independence Ave, Boumerdes 35000, Algeria.
