   Tan, Chaolin, Soochow Univ, Inst Met Mat \& Intelligent Mfg, Sch Iron \& Steel, Suzhou 215137, Peoples R China.
   Su, Jinlong; Jiang, Fulin; Li, Qinzhi, Hunan Univ, Coll Mat Sci \& Engn, State Key Lab Cemented Carbide, Changsha 410082, Peoples R China.
   Su, Jinlong; Sing, Swee Leong, Natl Univ Singapore, Dept Mech Engn, 9 Engn Dr 1, Singapore 117575, Singapore.
