   Aittokallio, Tero; Tanoli, Ziaurrehman, Univ Helsinki, iCAN Digital Precis Canc Med Flagship, Helsinki 00014, Finland.
   Aittokallio, Tero; Tanoli, Ziaurrehman, Helsinki Univ Hosp, Helsinki 00014, Finland.
   Aittokallio, Tero, Oslo Univ Hosp, Inst Canc Res, Dept Canc Genet, N-0379 Oslo, Norway.
   Aittokallio, Tero, Univ Oslo, Fac Med, Oslo Ctr Biostat \& Epidemiol OCBE, N-0372 Oslo, Norway.
   Tanoli, Ziaurrehman, Biocenter, Drug Discovery \& Chem Biol DDCB Consortium, Helsinki 00014, Finland.
