   Jeong, Incheol; Roh, Ki-Min, KIGAM, Resources Utilizat Res Ctr, Daejeon 34132, South Korea.
   Jeong, Incheol; Oh, Seeun; Lee, Kang Taek, Korea Adv Inst Sci \& Technol, Dept Mech Engn, Daejeon 34141, South Korea.
