   Fujii, Keisuke, RIKEN Ctr Adv Intelligence Project, Fukuoka, Fukuoka, Japan.
   Fujii, Keisuke, Japan Sci \& Technol Agcy, PRESTO, Kawaguchi, Saitama, Japan.},
